tag_list: architecture, architecture-buildings, architecture-projects, design, product-design, furniture-design, art, contemporary-art, contemporary-design, eco-design, cool-design, design-products, design-furniture, modern-architecture, contemporary-architecture,
overview:
Designitecture is an amazing blog about contemporary art, product design, furniture design, architecture projects and architecture buildings.

To connect art, architecture and design in a single website. To put them together and get a greater picture of these three creative disciplines that are so intertwined with each other. To do it in a way that nobody has seen before. Approaching each of the disciplines with the same passion and accuracy, innovating every day to offer the freshest and most original content. A platform to promote and broadcast contemporary culture from architects to architects, designers, artists and whoever is interested in acquiring inventive knowledge.
